{"type":"message","id":"86803bb0","parentId":"f1cba02b","timestamp":"2026-03-27T01:19:43.748Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"7位员工的确认版全部发送完毕。现在汇总给姚总，让他确认。","thinkingSignature":"c1388500a41a788e6dd644327f0498ba51a7ecf573ea756dd13e88ccdb19ae60"},{"type":"text","text":"7位员工确认版已全部发送完成。\n\n**汇总：**\n| 员工 | 部门 | 总分 | 等级 |\n|------|------|------|------|\n| 王文强 | 销售部 | 68分 | D |\n| 王垣皓 | 销售部 | 67分 | D |\n| 郝彦艳 | 商务部 | 77分 | C |\n| 李文娅 | 商务部 | 85分 | B |\n| 刘晓 | 商务部 | 82分 | B |\n| 胡文正 | 运维部 | 80分 | B |\n| 刘世龙 | 运维部 | 61分 | D |\n\n请姚总确认是否发送，确认后我立即发送给每位员工，并完成知识库归档。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":31312,"output":177,"cacheRead":57011,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":88500,"cost":{"input":0.0093936,"output":0.00021239999999999999,"cacheRead":0.00171033,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01131633}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774574373609}}
