{"type":"message","id":"4cd277ac","parentId":"bc823288","timestamp":"2026-03-27T01:29:30.318Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"7位员工全部发送完成。现在需要进行第7步：知识库归档。\n\n归档3步法：\n1. 确认版文档 → 创建到知识库\n2. 多维表格录入 → 录入27个字段\n3. 汇总索引更新 → 更新汇总文档\n\n让我先执行归档，然后向姚总确认发送完成。","thinkingSignature":"2eb911f8605d0a2a77f66bc34aecec6c4b46da945630c57c593dc39588ced40d"},{"type":"text","text":"7位员工已全部发送完成。现在执行知识库归档。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ok690kpl8euv_1","name":"feishu_wiki_space_node","arguments":{"action":"list","space_id":"7618965559127903161","page_size":20}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":42103,"output":142,"cacheRead":57011,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":99256,"cost":{"input":0.012630899999999999,"output":0.0001704,"cacheRead":0.00171033,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.014511629999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774574965159}}
