{"type":"message","id":"76cd47fa","parentId":"592cfdd1","timestamp":"2026-03-27T05:49:28.732Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"任务创建成功。我需要通知刘晓，但刘晓的任务是通过飞书任务系统下发的，她应该会收到通知。不过为了确保刘晓明确知道这个任务，我应该通过消息告知她。让我用 feishu_im_user_message 给她发一条消息。","thinkingSignature":"fa2c4f13080b4ec1831e4c522913822ba48c000e9c6821f2ad589ff5b7deda2a"},{"type":"text","text":"任务已创建。同时告知刘晓。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_xs4cpnd56z23_1","name":"feishu_im_user_message","arguments":{"action":"send","receive_id_type":"open_id","receive_id":"ou_2c47b54a9dbdbd13729a411a625283a1","msg_type":"text","content":"{\"text\":\"**道简网络总经理助理**：姚总下发任务——请今天与梁娜沟通之前撤资的事情，了解当前进度情况，并及时反馈。\\n\\n任务已同步至您的飞书任务列表，请查收并尽快处理。\"}"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":65190,"output":210,"cacheRead":57011,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":122411,"cost":{"input":0.019556999999999998,"output":0.000252,"cacheRead":0.00171033,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.021519329999999996}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774590561560}}
