{"type":"message","id":"7ae1daf9","parentId":"3252f362","timestamp":"2026-03-27T05:49:33.421Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"任务已创建并通知刘晓。向姚总汇报。","thinkingSignature":"1199cc2917a265ea3c121669c78f4e27ac632d41b6b915bfe472674e91bc90e6"},{"type":"text","text":"已完成：\n1. **飞书任务已创建** → 分配给刘晓，今日需完成\n2. **消息已发送** → 刘晓已收到通知\n\n姚总，请问还需要补充其他要求吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":65486,"output":61,"cacheRead":57011,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":122558,"cost":{"input":0.019645799999999998,"output":0.00007319999999999999,"cacheRead":0.00171033,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.021429329999999996}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774590569323}}
{"type":"message","id":"24306662","parentId":"7ae1daf9","timestamp":"2026-03-27T05:49:35.699Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-27 13:49:34 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | 姚霖 (ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b) [msg:om_x100b5355e801d4c4b27ec4f23cf4c37]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5355e801d4c4b27ec4f23cf4c37\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n  \"sender\": \"姚霖\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-03-27 13:49 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"姚霖 (ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n  \"name\": \"姚霖\"\n}\n```\n\nhttps://github.com/xianyu110/awesome-openclaw-tutorial"}],"timestamp":1774590575695}}
{"type":"message","id":"e7b7a7a3","parentId":"24306662","timestamp":"2026-03-27T05:49:40.723Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"姚总发了一个GitHub链接，是关于OpenClaw教程的。让我获取一下这个页面的内容，看看是什么。","thinkingSignature":"028a4fc94ab0abd9134ea807ee3b9444317dfa304b1a44572165ae609d23bb40"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_qil5at6fyb86_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-fetch/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":137,"output":69,"cacheRead":121140,"cacheWrite":1284,"totalTokens":122630,"cost":{"input":0.000041099999999999996,"output":0.0000828,"cacheRead":0.0036341999999999998,"cacheWrite":0.00015408,"total":0.0039121799999999995}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774590575697}}
{"type":"message","id":"ad8bd639","parentId":"e7b7a7a3","timestamp":"2026-03-27T05:49:40.822Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_qil5at6fyb86_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-fetch\r\ndescription: \"Use when user needs to crawl or fetch a specific URL to extract/summarize its content. Provides necessary command usage instructions for fetching known URLs. 触发词：网页抓取, 抓取网页, 提取网页内容, web crawl, 爬取, fetch url, 总结网页, 抓取 URL, 读取网页\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_fetch\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Fetch\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` 抓取指定网页内容，由 AI 自动总结/提取。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--url` | 网页 URL | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary（见 miaoda-web-search skill）\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL（见 miaoda-web-search skill）→ web-crawl 提取详情\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 抓取指定 URL 并提取信息\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli web-crawl --url https://example.com/pricing\r\n\r\n# 搜索 → 深入抓取：先搜索找到目标 URL，再抓取提取详细信息\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli web-crawl --url <搜索结果中的URL>\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`（见 miaoda-web-search skill） |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774590580775}}
{"type":"message","id":"ce753310","parentId":"ad8bd639","timestamp":"2026-03-27T05:49:44.197Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"让我抓取这个GitHub页面看看内容。","thinkingSignature":"db5b866368378a4be9541f8d549fbb0cc5c78493a949a902b612842bc4ef2684"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_tirmequ3jqki_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl --url https://github.com/xianyu110/awesome-openclaw-tutorial","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":66097,"output":68,"cacheRead":57011,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":123176,"cost":{"input":0.0198291,"output":0.00008159999999999999,"cacheRead":0.00171033,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.02162103}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774590580820}}
